  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>you turned into a worm.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>your boyfriend left you.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>you have to kill him.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'd KILL YOU as a worm is a difficult platformer where you've been turned into a worm and have to navigate the world in order to find and take out your boyfriend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >an open world that you <strong>have</strong> to climb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a worm with a lot of love who needs to climb it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >around 2 hours of climbing content (if you're good enough)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a lot of easy jumps that you will fail.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >also a couple of bees and a bird</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape The Dirt</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/12eb2f898e94686d856265a65760280a.poster.avif?t=1755331644\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/12eb2f898e94686d856265a65760280a.webm?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/12eb2f898e94686d856265a65760280a.mp4?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Return To The Dirt</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/7e8dc854f46229bce2d967223c7c5f9a.poster.avif?t=1755331644\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/7e8dc854f46229bce2d967223c7c5f9a.webm?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/7e8dc854f46229bce2d967223c7c5f9a.mp4?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's a Vicious Cycle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/ac5cdc45ce2568da177dd1eea254e642.poster.avif?t=1755331644\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/ac5cdc45ce2568da177dd1eea254e642.webm?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/ac5cdc45ce2568da177dd1eea254e642.mp4?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>you turned into a worm.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>your boyfriend left you.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>you have to kill him.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'd KILL YOU as a worm is a difficult platformer where you've been turned into a worm and have to navigate the world in order to find and take out your boyfriend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >an open world that you <strong>have</strong> to climb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a worm with a lot of love who needs to climb it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >around 2 hours of climbing content (if you're good enough)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a lot of easy jumps that you will fail.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >also a couple of bees and a bird</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape The Dirt</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/12eb2f898e94686d856265a65760280a.poster.avif?t=1755331644\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/12eb2f898e94686d856265a65760280a.webm?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351470/extras/12eb2f898e94686d856265a65760280a.mp4?t=1755331644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Return To The Dirt</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps